				<thingDef>ComponentSimple</thingDef>
				<count>10</count>
			</li>
			<li>
				<thingDef>MechanismSimple</thingDef>
				<count>10</count>
			</li>
		</thingsCount>
		<effectDescription>The construction increases the number of culture points once. Allies and neutrals will not visit. Enemies seek to destroy. It can contain 1 pawn inside. The range of the field of view, which opens with the tower, depends on the skill of her ranged combat. If there is no pawn in the tower, it does not work.</effectDescription>
		<minConstructionSkill>3</minConstructionSkill>
		<buildCost>20000</buildCost>
		<mapTag>MilitaryObject_Signal_Tower</mapTag>
		<worker>ProjectParagon.Core.WorldObjects.CulturalSiteWorker_Signal_Tower</worker>
		<sitePriorityForHostile>65</sitePriorityForHostile>
		<sitePriorityForNeutral>0</sitePriorityForNeutral>
		<sitePriorityForAlly>0</sitePriorityForAlly>
		<maxCaravanTechLevel>Industrial</maxCaravanTechLevel>
		<cultureMultiplierByTechLevel>
			<points>
				<li>(0, 1)</li>
